### Hadith 3:292

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

The Prophet said, "There was a merchant who used to lend the people, and
whenever his debtor was in straitened circumstances, he would say to his
employees, 'Forgive him so that Allah may forgive us.' So, Allah forgave
him."

